\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9923787 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1402753\charrsid5841043 Could you ask for a second helping if there was one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607039 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1402753\charrsid5841043 
Well they'd give you a second helping if there was any left if you want, to get rid of it, yes. Yes, yes. There was nothing spoiled in - in those days, no, no, no.
