\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607039 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1402753\charrsid5841043 We - I don't think I had a lot of toys, I - I - I don't think I had a lot of toys. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9923787 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1402753\charrsid5841043 In some families a meal was a very formal occasion.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607039 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1402753\charrsid5841043 Yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9923787 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1402753\charrsid5841043 It wasn't like that in your case?
